---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { site } from '../data/site';

const updated = '2026-05-24';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description={`How ${site.name} handles personal information on this website.`}
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 pt-12 pb-16">
    <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-accent-2)]">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl mt-2 tracking-wide">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-dim)] mt-2">Last updated: {updated}</p>

    <div class="prose mt-8 text-[var(--color-text)] leading-relaxed space-y-5">
      <p>
        This site is operated by Najdorf Esports (the "Organization"). The legal entity
        behind the Organization is being formalized; this notice will be updated to
        name the operating company once registration is complete.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-8 tracking-wide">What we collect</h2>
      <p>
        This site does not set analytics cookies, advertising trackers, or
        first-party tracking pixels. Pages are static HTML, CSS, and a small
        amount of vanilla JavaScript for the match countdown, mobile navigation,
        and a client-side hero swap on match day.
      </p>

      <p>
        Our hosting provider (Cloudflare Pages) records access logs that include
        your IP address, user agent, and the URLs you request. Cloudflare retains
        these logs for security and abuse-prevention purposes. We do not link
        these logs to any personal identity and do not use them for marketing.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-8 tracking-wide">Fonts</h2>
      <p>
        Display and body fonts (Anton, Inter) are served directly from this
        domain. No font requests are sent to Google, Adobe, or other third-party
        font CDNs.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-8 tracking-wide">Embedded video player</h2>
      <p>
        During an active match window (roughly 30 minutes before kickoff through
        three hours after), the home page may load a Twitch player from
        <code>player.twitch.tv</code> so visitors can watch the stream inline.
        Outside that window no iframe is loaded and no request is made to Twitch.
      </p>
      <p>
        When the player is loaded, Twitch sets its own cookies and may collect
        usage data per its own policies. We do not control these cookies or
        receive their contents. See
        <a href="https://www.twitch.tv/p/legal/privacy-notice/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Twitch's Privacy Notice</a>
        for details. If you do not want the Twitch player to load, leave the home
        page before the live window or open the stream link directly on Twitch
        in a separate session.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-8 tracking-wide">Outbound links</h2>
      <p>
        Player profiles link to third-party sites (Twitter / X, Twitch,
        Liquipedia) when those handles are available. Clicking an outbound link
        takes you to that site, whose own privacy practices apply once you arrive.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-8 tracking-wide">Email contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you email us at {site.contactEmail}, we will store the contents of your
        message and your email address for as long as is reasonably needed to
        respond and keep records of the correspondence.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-8 tracking-wide">Your rights</h2>
      <p>
        Depending on where you live, you may have the right to request a copy of any
        personal data we hold about you, request that we delete it, or ask us to
        correct it. Reach us at {site.contactEmail}.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-8 tracking-wide">Changes</h2>
      <p>
        We will update the "Last updated" date above when this policy changes.
        Material changes will be announced in the news section.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style is:global>
  .prose p { margin-bottom: 1em; }
  .prose a { color: var(--color-accent-2); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; }
  .prose a:hover { color: var(--color-accent); }
</style>
